&CONTROL
    calculation='scf'
    prefix='NiO'
    restart_mode='from_scratch'
    outdir='./NiO'
    pseudo_dir='./'
    tprnfor   = .true.
    verbosity = 'high'
/
&system
    ibrav = 0, celldm(1) = 9.6715
    nat = 4, ntyp = 3, nspin=2,
    ecutwfc = 50.0
    starting_magnetization(1)=  0.2,
    starting_magnetization(2)= -0.2,
    tot_magnetization = 0.0,
    nbnd=28, 
    occupations = 'smearing',
    smearing = 'gauss',
    degauss=0.01, 
 /
 &electrons
    mixing_beta = 0.3,
    conv_thr = 1d-10
 /
CELL_PARAMETERS {alat}
0.288675  -0.166667   0.942809  
0.000000   0.333333   0.942809   
-0.288675  -0.166667   0.942809  

ATOMIC_SPECIES
Ni1 58.6934   Ni_ONCV_PBE-1.2_wfc.upf
Ni2  58.6934   Ni_ONCV_PBE-1.2_wfc.upf
O  15.999   O_ONCV_PBE-1.2.upf

ATOMIC_POSITIONS crystal
Ni1  0.0000000000  0.0000000000  0.0000000000
Ni2  0.5000000000  0.5000000000  0.5000000000
O  0.7500000000  0.7500000000  0.7500000000
O  0.2500000000  0.2500000000  0.2500000000

K_POINTS automatic
3 3 3 0 0 0

HUBBARD {atomic}
U Ni1-3d 6.3
U Ni2-3d 6.3